  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/b5c35d818f10e0a5.jpg?v=1782530565\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Hi - You may be coming here from <a href=\"http://lilithandscrap.blogspot.com/\">Lilith's blog</a>, or you may just be a regular. Either way, welcome! It's already the 22nd of the month once again. Some of the Garden Girls from <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/whats-hot/%3Fpp%3D300\">Two Peas In A Bucket</a> are doing a little blog hop.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/71f332a2fe34daaf.jpg?v=1782530568\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/8c1baad3b8e562c8.jpg?v=1782530570\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>It's a focus on photos and I couldn't resist using a little <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/crate-paper/138963-maggie-holmes-fabric-bows/%3Ffilters%3D_maggie_holmes_\">Maggie Holmes Crate Paper bow</a> along with <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/139072-life-yes-please-amy-tangerine-sticker-book/%3Ffilters%3D_yes_please_\">these stickers</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/ae81ef3dc3a52aff.jpg?v=1782530573\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>1. Everything by Heidi Swapp, really, but <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/heidi-swapp/141410-clear-pop-clear-mint-alphabet/%3Ffilters%3Dwhats-hot\">these alphas</a> are perfection. Hoping she comes out with more colors.</p><p>2. <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/simple-stories/141305-snp-daily-stamps/%3Ffilters%3Dwhats-hot\">sn@p! Daily Stamps</a>, perfect for every day layouts and Project Life.</p><p>3. Chic Tags <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/chic-tags/141034-road-trip-mini-tags/%3Ffilters%3Dwhats-hot\">mini road trip tags</a></p><p>4.<a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/hero-arts/138023-ocean-dye-ink-pad/%3Ffilters%3D_hero_arts_\"> Hero Arts Ocean Dye Ink </a>- May be the most perfect teal/turquoise ink ever.</p><p>5. <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/uni-ball/93930-uni-ball-signo-gel-pen-broad-point/%3Ffilters%3Dwhats-hot\">Uni-ball Signo white gel pen</a>- Trust me, the only white gel pen you need. In fact, I highly recommend stocking up.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/6cce3499bb2b5582.jpg?v=1782530576\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>This layout by Orangegearle using my newest release with American Crafts - <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/_yes_please_/%3Fpp%3D300%26avad%3D41735_e3db8e21\">Yes, Please</a> along with some chalk and plenty of color. Love it.Next stop is <a href=\"http://www.marcypenner.com/\">Marcy Penner.</a> The last stop on the hop is <a href=\"http://twopeasinabucket.typepad.com/\">Two Peas blog</a> where you will also see the entire list of participants.</p>"
}